msg: This class had a protected field that was hiding a protected field in its parent class. A subclass of this
class (OsgiMiniProjectizer) referenced the field, but it wasn't getting the parent's version (which was
initialized) - instead it got J2EEMiniProjectizer's version, which was not initialized. This caused an NPE
